---
import { PRICE_ANCHOR, PRICE_BASIC, formatPrice, CHECKOUT_BASIC } from '../config/pricing';
---
<section id="preco" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-4 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 50%, #f1f5f9 100%);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-30">
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-[#4CAF50]" style="filter: blur(120px);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-[#2C3E99]" style="filter: blur(100px);"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mb-2">Oferta Especial</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-[#4CAF50] font-bold mb-6">Acesso vitalício ao Ebook completo</p>

    {/* Desconstrução de Valor */}
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">💡 Vamos fazer as contas do valor real:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-3">
          <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-400 line-through">R$ 300</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Consultoria pedagógica<br/>1 hora</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#4CAF50]/10 rounded-xl p-3 border-2 border-[#4CAF50]">
          <p class="text-2xl font-black text-[#4CAF50]">200h</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-700">Você economiza<br/>por ano (5h/semana)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#4CAF50]/10 rounded-xl p-3 border-2 border-[#4CAF50]">
          <p class="text-2xl font-black text-[#4CAF50]">R$ 47</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-700">Investimento único<br/>vitalício</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 text-center">
        <strong>Em um ano, você economiza 200 horas</strong> de planejamento — o equivalente a <strong>R$ 60.000</strong> em valor de consultoria.
        <br/>Investir <strong class="text-[#4CAF50]">R$ 47</strong> para economizar milhares é o melhor negócio da sua carreira.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border-4 border-[#4CAF50] p-8 shadow-2xl relative" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #fff 30%, #f7fee7 100%); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.25);">
        <span class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4CAF50] to-[#2E7D32] text-white text-sm font-black px-5 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg">OFERTA ÚNICA</span>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#4CAF50] uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Ebook Completo</p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4CAF50]/20 to-[#2E7D32]/10 border-2 border-[#4CAF50]/40 py-5 px-4 mb-6">
          <p class="line-through text-gray-500 text-sm">De R$ {PRICE_ANCHOR},00</p>
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-[#2C3E99]">R$ {formatPrice(PRICE_BASIC)},00</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mt-1">ou 3x de R$ 15,67 sem juros</p>
          <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-[#4CAF50] text-white text-xs font-bold">Economize R$ 100</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold">✓</span> Ebook completo (360 páginas, 60 por bloco)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold">✓</span> 25+ atividades detalhadas passo a passo</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold">✓</span> 3 projetos interdisciplinares completos</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold">✓</span> Templates e checklists editáveis</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#4CAF50] font-bold">✓</span> Acesso vitalício + atualizações gratuitas</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={CHECKOUT_BASIC} class="js-open-checkout-modal block w-full text-center text-white font-black text-xl py-5 rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 active:scale-[0.98]" style="background:#2E7D32; box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #1a4d1e;">
          QUERO GARANTIR MEU EBOOK!
        </a>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1 mt-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-700 font-semibold">⏰ Oferta expira em:</p>
          <p id="timer-preco" class="text-xl font-black text-[#4CAF50] tabular-nums" role="timer" aria-live="polite">05:00</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Custo de não comprar */}
    <div class="mt-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-100 to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-center">⚠️ O custo de NÃO ter este material:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-red-500">•</span>
          <span>Continuar passando fins de semana planejando (mais 200h de trabalho não pago por ano)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-red-500">•</span>
          <span>Stress constante por não ter atividades prontas na segunda-feira</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-red-500">•</span>
          <span>Perder oportunidades de reconhecimento profissional</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-red-500">•</span>
          <span>Alunos menos engajados por falta de atividades estruturadas</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-900 font-bold mt-4">R$ 47 é menos que um jantar fora. Mas pode transformar sua rotina para sempre.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  (function () {
    const el = document.getElementById('timer-preco');
    if (!el) return;
    let segundos = 5 * 60; // 05:00
    function atualizar() {
      if (segundos < 0) return;
      const m = Math.floor(segundos / 60);
      const s = segundos % 60;
      el.textContent = String(m).padStart(2, '0') + ':' + String(s).padStart(2, '0');
      segundos--;
      if (segundos >= 0) setTimeout(atualizar, 1000);
    }
    atualizar();
  })();
</script>
